msgstr "``Dodato u 3.44``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:275
msgid ""
"Uses a method proposed by Wang & Liu to identify and fill surface "
"depressions in digital elevation models."
msgstr ""
"Koristi metod koji su predložili Wang & Liu za prepoznavanje i popunjavanje "
"depresija površine u digitalnim modelima visina."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:277
msgid ""
"The method was enhanced to allow the creation of hydrologically sound "
"elevation models, i.e. not only to fill the depression(s) but also to "
"preserve a downward slope along the flow path. If desired, this is "
"accomplished by preserving a minimum slope gradient (and thus elevation "
"difference) between cells."
msgstr ""
"Metod je unapređen da omogući pravljenje hidrološki ispravnih modela visina,"
" tj. ne samo da popuni depresije, već i da očuva nizbrdi nagib duž toka. Ako"
" se želi, to se postiže očuvanjem minimalnog gradijenta nagiba (a time i "
"razlike u visini) između ćelija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:281
msgid ""
"*References: Wang, L. & H. Liu (2006): An efficient method for identifying "
"and filling surface depressions in digital elevation models for hydrologic "
"analysis and modelling. International Journal of Geographical Information "
"Science, Vol. 20, No. 2: 193-213.*"
msgstr ""
"*Reference: Wang, L. & H. Liu (2006): An efficient method for identifying "
"and filling surface depressions in digital elevation models for hydrologic "
"analysis and modelling. International Journal of Geographical Information "
"Science, Vol. 20, No. 2: 193-213.*"

