msgstr "Azimut i vertikalni ugao"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:443
msgid ""
"The hillshade layer contains values from 0 (complete shadow) to 255 "
"(complete sun). Hillshade is used usually to better understand the relief of"
" the area."
msgstr ""
"Sloj osenčenog reljefa sadrži vrednosti od 0 (potpuna senka) do 255 (potpuno"
" sunce). Osenčeni reljef se obično koristi za bolje razumevanje reljefa "
"oblasti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:450
msgid "Hillshade layer with azimuth 300 and vertical angle 45"
msgstr "Sloj osenčenog reljefa sa azimutom 300 i vertikalnim uglom 45"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:452
msgid ""
"Particularly interesting is to give the hillshade layer a transparency value"
" and overlap it with the elevation raster:"
msgstr ""
"Posebno je zanimljivo dodeliti sloju osenčenog reljefa vrednost prozirnosti "
"i preklopiti ga sa visinskim rasterom:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:458
