#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:545
msgid "Hypsometric curves"
msgstr "Hipsometrijske krive"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:546
msgid ""
"Calculates hypsometric curves for an input Digital Elevation Model. Curves "
"are produced as CSV files in an output folder specified by the user."
msgstr ""
"Računa hipsometrijske krive za ulazni digitalni model visina. Krive se prave"
" kao CSV datoteke u izlaznom folderu koji zadaje korisnik."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:550
msgid ""
"A hypsometric curve is a cumulative histogram of elevation values in a "
"geographical area."
msgstr ""
"Hipsometrijska kriva je kumulativni histogram vrednosti visina u geografskoj"
" oblasti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:553
msgid ""
"You can use hypsometric curves to detect differences in the landscape due to"
" the geomorphology of the territory."
msgstr ""
"Hipsometrijske krive možete koristiti za otkrivanje razlika u predelu usled "
"geomorfologije teritorije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:568
msgid "**DEM to analyze**"
msgstr "**DEM za analizu**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:569
msgid "``INPUT_DEM``"
msgstr "``INPUT_DEM``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:571
msgid "Digital Terrain Model raster layer to use for calculating altitudes"
msgstr ""
"Rasterski sloj digitalnog modela terena koji se koristi za računanje "
"nadmorskih visina"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:573
msgid "**Boundary layer**"
msgstr "**Sloj granica**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:574
msgid "``BOUNDARY_LAYER``"
msgstr "``BOUNDARY_LAYER``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:575
msgid "[vector: polygon]"
msgstr "[vektor: poligon]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:576
msgid ""
"Polygon vector layer with boundaries of areas used to calculate hypsometric "
"curves"
msgstr ""
"Poligonski vektorski sloj sa granicama oblasti koje se koriste za računanje "
"hipsometrijskih krivih"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:578
msgid "**Step**"
msgstr "**Korak**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:579
msgid "``STEP``"
msgstr "``STEP``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:582
msgid "Default: 100.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 100.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:583
msgid "Vertical distance between curves"
msgstr "Vertikalno rastojanje između krivih"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:584
#, python-format
msgid "**Use % of area instead of absolute value**"
msgstr "**Koristi % površine umesto apsolutne vrednosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:585
msgid "``USE_PERCENTAGE``"
msgstr "``USE_PERCENTAGE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:586
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:681
msgid "[boolean]"
msgstr "[logička vrednost]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:588
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:683
msgid "Default: False"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: False"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:589
msgid ""
"Write area percentage to “Area” field of the CSV file instead of the "
"absolute area"
msgstr ""
"Upiši procenat površine u polje „Area“ CSV datoteke umesto apsolutne "
"površine"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:591
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:613
msgid "**Hypsometric curves**"
msgstr "**Hipsometrijske krive**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:592
