msgid "[folder]"
msgstr "[folder]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:594
msgid ""
"Specify the output folder for the hypsometric curves. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni folder za hipsometrijske krive. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

