msgid "Save to a Temporary Directory"
msgstr "Sačuvaj u privremeni direktorijum"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:4
msgid "Save to Directory"
msgstr "Sačuvaj u direktorijum"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:616
msgid ""
"Directory containing the files with the hypsometric curves. For each feature"
" from the input vector layer, a CSV file with area and altitude values will "
"be created."
msgstr ""
"Direktorijum koji sadrži datoteke sa hipsometrijskim krivama. Za svaki "
"objekat iz ulaznog vektorskog sloja biće napravljena CSV datoteka sa "
"vrednostima površine i nadmorske visine."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:621
msgid ""
"The file names start with ``histogram_``, followed by layer name and feature"
" ID."
msgstr ""
"Nazivi datoteka počinju sa ``histogram_``, praćeni nazivom sloja i ID-jem "
"objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:631
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:hypsometriccurves``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:hypsometriccurves``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:641
msgid "Relief"
msgstr "Reljef"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:642
msgid ""
"Creates a shaded relief layer from digital elevation data. You can specify "
"the relief color manually, or you can let the algorithm choose automatically"
" all the relief classes."
msgstr ""
"Pravi sloj osenčenog reljefa iz digitalnih podataka o visinama. Boju reljefa"
" možete zadati ručno, ili možete pustiti algoritam da automatski izabere sve"
" klase reljefa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:649
msgid "Relief layer"
msgstr "Sloj reljefa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:679
msgid "**Generate relief classes automatically**"
msgstr "**Generiši klase reljefa automatski**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:680
msgid "``AUTO_COLORS``"
msgstr "``AUTO_COLORS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:684
msgid ""
"If you check this option the algorithm will create all the relief color "
"classes automatically"
msgstr ""
"Ako uključite ovu opciju, algoritam će automatski napraviti sve klase boja "
"reljefa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:686
msgid "**Relief colors**"
msgstr "**Boje reljefa**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:689
msgid "``COLORS``"
msgstr "``COLORS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:690
msgid "[table widget]"
msgstr "[vidžet tabele]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:691
msgid ""
"Use the table widget if you want to choose the relief colors manually. You "
"can add as many color classes as you want: for each class you can choose the"
" lower and upper bound and finally by clicking on the color row you can "
"choose the color thanks to the color widget."
msgstr ""
"Koristite vidžet tabele ako želite ručno da izaberete boje reljefa. Možete "
"dodati koliko god klasa boja želite: za svaku klasu možete izabrati donju i "
"gornju granicu i, klikom na red boje, izabrati boju pomoću vidžeta za boje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:701
msgid "Manually setting of relief color classes"
msgstr "Ručno postavljanje klasa boja reljefa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:703
msgid ""
"The buttons in the right side panel give you the chance to: add or remove "
"color classes, change the order of the color classes already defined, open "
"an existing file with color classes and save the current classes as file."
msgstr ""
"Dugmad u desnom bočnom panelu daju vam mogućnost da: dodate ili uklonite "
"klase boja, promenite redosled već definisanih klasa boja, otvorite "
"postojeću datoteku sa klasama boja i sačuvate trenutne klase kao datoteku."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:708
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:745
msgid "**Relief**"
msgstr "**Reljef**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:713
msgid ""
"Specify the output relief raster layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni rasterski sloj reljefa. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

