"Specify the CSV table for the output frequency distribution. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte CSV tabelu za izlaznu raspodelu učestalosti. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:748
msgid "The output relief raster layer"
msgstr "Izlazni rasterski sloj reljefa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:752
msgid "The output frequency distribution"
msgstr "Izlazna raspodela učestalosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:757
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:relief``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:relief``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:767
msgid "Ruggedness index"
msgstr "Indeks razuđenosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:768
msgid ""
"Calculates the quantitative measurement of terrain heterogeneity described "
"by Riley et al. (1999). It is calculated for every location, by summarizing "
"the change in elevation within the 3x3 pixel grid."
msgstr ""
"Računa kvantitativnu meru heterogenosti terena koju su opisali Riley i "
"saradnici (1999). Računa se za svaku lokaciju sabiranjem promene visine "
"unutar mreže piksela 3x3."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:773
msgid ""
"Each pixel contains the difference in elevation from a center cell and the 8"
" cells surrounding it."
msgstr ""
"Svaki piksel sadrži razliku u visini između centralne ćelije i 8 ćelija koje"
" je okružuju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:779
msgid "Ruggedness layer from low (red) to high values (green)"
msgstr "Sloj razuđenosti od niskih (crveno) do visokih vrednosti (zeleno)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:802
msgid ""
"Vertical exaggeration. This parameter is useful when the Z units differ from"
" the X and Y units, for example feet and meters. You can use this parameter "
"to adjust for this. Increasing the value of this parameter will exaggerate "
"the final result (making it look more rugged). The default is 1 (no "
"exaggeration)."
msgstr ""
"Vertikalno preuveličavanje. Ovaj parametar je koristan kada se Z jedinice "
"razlikuju od X i Y jedinica, na primer stope i metri. Ovim parametrom to "
"možete prilagoditi. Povećanje vrednosti ovog parametra preuveličaće konačni "
"rezultat (čineći ga razuđenijim). Podrazumevano je 1 (bez preuveličavanja)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:809
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:832
msgid "**Ruggedness**"
msgstr "**Razuđenost**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:814
msgid ""
"Specify the output ruggedness raster layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni rasterski sloj razuđenosti. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:835
msgid "The output ruggedness raster layer"
msgstr "Izlazni rasterski sloj razuđenosti"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:840
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:ruggednessindex``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:ruggednessindex``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:850
msgid "Slope"
msgstr "Nagib"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:851
msgid ""
"Calculates the slope from an input raster layer. The slope is the angle of "
"inclination of the terrain and is expressed in **degrees**."
msgstr ""
"Računa nagib iz ulaznog rasterskog sloja. Nagib je ugao nagnutosti terena i "
"izražava se u **stepenima**."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:857
msgid "Flat areas in red, steep areas in blue"
msgstr "Ravne oblasti crveno, strme oblasti plavo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:880
msgid ""
"Vertical exaggeration. This parameter is useful when the Z units differ from"
" the X and Y units, for example feet and meters. You can use this parameter "
"to adjust for this. Increasing the value of this parameter will exaggerate "
"the final result (making it steeper). The default is 1 (no exaggeration)."
msgstr ""
"Vertikalno preuveličavanje. Ovaj parametar je koristan kada se Z jedinice "
"razlikuju od X i Y jedinica, na primer stope i metri. Ovim parametrom to "
"možete prilagoditi. Povećanje vrednosti ovog parametra preuveličaće konačni "
"rezultat (čineći ga strmijim). Podrazumevano je 1 (bez preuveličavanja)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:887
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:910
msgid "**Slope**"
msgstr "**Nagib**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:892
msgid ""
"Specify the output slope raster layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni rasterski sloj nagiba. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:913
msgid "The output slope raster layer"
msgstr "Izlazni rasterski sloj nagiba"

